(897,1,'2026-03-19 03:17:04','2026-03-19 03:17:04','<h2>About Me</h2>\r\nWelcome to my portfolio!\r\n<p style=\"border-left-color: #e8534e; padding: 0 0 0 1rem; border-left-style: solid;\">I am a User Interface &amp; Concept Artist with 10+ years of experience in the video game industry, specializing in UI/UX design and concept art. As a game artist, I have helped deliver AAA-level assets and artwork that has shaped player experiences across live service and narrative-driven titles. Combining a lifelong passion for games and knowledge with my design expertise, I create UI that is both intuitive and visually immersive, enhancing player engagement while staying true to a game’s identity.</p>\r\nPlease reach out if you are interested in working together!\r\n<h2>Technical Skills</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>10+ years of experience working in the video game industry. 5+ years of AAA.</li>\r\n 	<li>Concept art for games specializing in character, hard surface, and environments.</li>\r\n 	<li>UI/UX design for web, mobile, console, and PC games with a focus on art.</li>\r\n 	<li>UI art asset generation for games and web using Unreal Engine and Unity.</li>\r\n 	<li>Project style guide generation and maintenance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Icon design, logo design, branding, and marketing assets.</li>\r\n 	<li>Proficient in semantic HTML, CSS, and JavaScript best practices for front end web development.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Software Expertise</strong>: Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, After Effects, InDesign, Blender, Zbrush, Keyshot, Marmoset, Perforce, Git</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Professional Experience</h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #e8534e; margin: 0px .4rem 0px 0px; font-weight: bold;\">|</span><strong>2017-2024\r\n</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Bebas Neue Regular\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.618rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: uppercase;\">Respawn Entertainment</span>\r\nSr UI/UX Designer, Sr Concept Artist, Graphic Designer\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #e8534e; margin: 0px .4rem 0px 0px; font-weight: bold;\">|</span> 2013-2017\r\n</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Bebas Neue Regular\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.618rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: uppercase;\">Section Studios\r\n</span>Sr 2D Artist, Lead UI/UX Designer\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #e8534e; margin: 0px .4rem 0px 0px; font-weight: bold;\">|</span> 2012-2025\r\n<span style=\"font-family: \'Bebas Neue Regular\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.618rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: uppercase;\">Freelance</span>\r\nUI/UX Design, Character Concept Art, Graphic Designer\r\n<h2>Education</h2>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #e8534e; margin: 0px .4rem 0px 0px; font-weight: bold;\">|</span> 2011-2018\r\n<span style=\"font-family: \'Bebas Neue Regular\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.618rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: uppercase;\">Non-accredited Courses</span>\r\nConcept Design Academy, Robotpencil, LearnSquared, CGHub, Gumroad, Brainstorm\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #e8534e; margin: 0px .4rem 0px 0px; font-weight: bold;\">|</span> 2011-2012</strong>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: \'Bebas Neue Regular\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.618rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: uppercase;\">Illustration</span>\r\n<strong>Art Center College of Design</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #e8534e; margin: 0px .4rem 0px 0px; font-weight: bold;\">|</span>2009-2011</strong>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: \'Bebas Neue Regular\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.618rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: uppercase;\">Graphic Design</span>\r\n<strong>Santa Barbara Community College</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #e8534e; margin: 0px .4rem 0px 0px; font-weight: bold;\">|</span> 2007-2009\r\n</strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Bebas Neue Regular\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.618rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0px; text-transform: uppercase;\">Computer Engineering</span>\r\nCal Poly San Luis Obispo\r\n<h2>Projects</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Star Wars: Arsenal (PC/Console, Cancled)</li>\r\n 	<li>Apex Legends (All Platforms)</li>\r\n 	<li>Awake (VR)</li>\r\n 	<li>Rival: Crimson x Chaos (Mobile)</li>\r\n 	<li>Covert (VR)</li>\r\n 	<li>House Flip (Mobile)</li>\r\n 	<li>Starblood Arena (PSVR)</li>\r\n 	<li>League of Legends (PC)</li>\r\n 	<li>The Art of Homeworld (Print)</li>\r\n 	<li>Disney Playmation (App/Product)</li>\r\n 	<li>Dead Realm (PC)</li>\r\n 	<li>Eclipse (VR)</li>\r\n 	<li>Zombie Killer Squad (Mobile)</li>\r\n 	<li>Tinertia (Console)</li>\r\n 	<li>Smart Runners (Mobile)</li>\r\n 	<li>Vlad: The Impaler (PC)</li>\r\n 	<li>Pinopolis (Mobile)</li>\r\n</ul>','Resume','','inherit','closed','closed','','338-revision-v1','','','2026-03-19 03:17:04','2026-03-19 03:17:04','',338,'https://brandonrp.test/?p=897',0,'revision','',0),
(898,1,'2026-03-19 03:22:28','2026-03-19 03:22:28','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:quote -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\r\n<p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:quote -->\r\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\r\n<p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://brandonrp.com/wp/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Front Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','817-revision-v1','','','2026-03-19 03:22:28','2026-03-19 03:22:28','',817,'https://brandonrp.test/?p=898',0,'revision','',0),
